divs: Sighting Detailsi was sitting in my room alone as i heard a loud noise in the sky, i rush to my window and see that my puppy willy is dead. As i run towards it a bright light from the sky structs me and sucks me into a spaceship. When i open my eyes i see a family of 5 that were aliens they were drinking willy's blood. As i scream like a lil bitch they hit me with a shoe and knocked my unconsions. When i woke up i notice my zipper was down and a strange marsion was smiling...
Summary: i was sitting in my room alone as i heard a loud noise in the sky
